<div class="FunctionDoc YAMLDoc" id="image-__init__" markdown="1">

## [function __image\.\_\_init\_\___\(form, path=None, frame=False, adjust=True\)](#function-__image__init____form-pathnone-framefalse-adjusttrue) {#function-__image__init____form-pathnone-framefalse-adjusttrue}

Constructor.

__Arguments:__

- `form` -- The parent form.
	- Type: form

__Keywords:__

- `path` -- The full path to the image. To show an image from the file pool, you need to first use `experiment.get_file` to determine the full path to the image.
	- Default: None
	- Type: str, unicode, NoneType
- `frame` -- Indicates whether a frame should be drawn around the widget.
	- Default: False
	- Type: bool
- `adjust` -- Indicates whether the image should be scaled according to the size of the widget.
	- Default: True
	- Type: bool

</div>

